<p style="text-align: center;">Â  101110<br />
+011100<br />
&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<br />
1 001010<br />
+ 1<br />
&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<br />
001011</p>
<p>Hence, substraction of A-B i.e 46 &#8211; 35 by using 1&#8217;s complement is 001011 Â i.e 11.</p>
